summary: An Ordinance appropriating the sum of $126.12 from the general fund to be paid into Local Improvement District Fund No. 243 to pay installments Nos. 2, 3, 4 and 5, with penalty and interest, due on lots 6 and 7, block 8, Compton's First Addition to the City of Seattle, assessed for the grading of 15th Avenue from East Columbia Street to Madison Street under Ordinance No. 5688.
